, a professor of Islamic religion, asked the Moslem community to remain calm. He said, `` We are a few days from the Ramadan,'' which Moslems mark with a month of fasting during the day. `` These are days for prayer. One must not seek revenge. The imam was a tolerant man, a generous man, he lent his money to several people.''
