ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION> and <ORGANIZATION> Chrysler </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION> also offer rebates or low interest rate incentives on a variety of their cars and trucks. Some of the <ORGANIZATION> GM </ORGANIZATION> offers expire as early as Monday. <ORGANIZATION> Chrysler </ORGANIZATION>'s incentives run indefinitely There was no immediate move by <ORGANIZATION> GM </ORGANIZATION> or <ORGANIZATION> Chrysler </ORGANIZATION> to match <ORGANIZATION> Ford </ORGANIZATION>'s new incentive package
