<HEAD>Stock Prices Edge Higher For Third Straight Gain</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: Updates with closing prices throughout.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By PETER COY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Business Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
